[h2 id=BcSQuestForTiresGrogSRevengeColecovision 
	"BC's Quest For Tires: Grog's Revenge (Colecovision)
	$LF
]h2
[div class=p 
	"Thor has completed his Quest for Tires. Now he must discover the Meaning Of Life, hidden away somewhere in a long maze of mountains. 
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The perilous roads around the mountains are covered with clams. Thor must gather 100 clams as he wheels his way along the 
	$LF
	"roads, then use the clams to pay Peter, the toll-taker, and advance to the next mountain. 
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The only way to the toll booth is through dark, scary caves. There are lots of clams in the caves for Thor to collect, but there are also sharp stalagmites to watch out for. Keep Thor's headlight sweeping back and forth for maximum clams. 
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Out of the cave, watch out for the grouchy Grog, who "shellfishly" saves clams for himself. And free-wheellng Thor must also contend with rocks, potholes and wheal-eating Tiredactyls in his quest for clams and the Meaning Of Life! 
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"More information about this game can be found in the manual: 
	[a href=https://archive.org/details/BCs_Quest_for_Tires_II_Grogs_Revenge_1984_Coleco rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"https://archive.org/details/BCs_Quest_for_Tires_II_Grogs_Revenge_1984_Coleco
	]a
	$LF
]div
