[h3 id=EffortInTasing 
	"Effort In TASing
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"A few years ago, I had started working on Grog's Revenge for the Commodore 64, but that version has a lot of difference and problems that I need to figure out. I have had this TAS done for awhile and I just can't figure out any way to make it faster. 
	$LF
	"There is only one issue...crossing paths with Grog on a level near the end. I had to basically wait for a few seconds before entering a tunnel. Having thought on this for a while, I realized that a solution is not surfacing for me to get past the only problem faster.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=RomIssue 
	"ROM Issue
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Originally, I had started with the ROM "BC's Quest for Tires II - Grog's Revenge (1984) (32k).col". Near the end, the game started freaking out. Bizhawk's hash, was showing confirmed...but I eventually had to go with "BC's Quest for Tires II - Grog's Revenge (1984) (24k) [a1].col"...which ended off fine. This ROM also showed a correct has in Bizhawk, which is why I decided to go with it.
	$LF
]div
